data.description:
Seller is offering 2% of sales price for a seller concessions (rate buy down)!!!!

Super Desirable Neighborhood: Charming 3BD/2BA, 2,234 total sqft Broomfield Ranch Home on a Huge Corner Lot.

This delightful property offers you a unique opportunity to make it your own with fresh new carpet and personal touches. With a high walk score and a very high sell score indicator, this home is an incredible find.

Property Highlights:

3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms
- Spacious 2,234 Sq. Ft. Home
- Attached 2-Car Garage
- Huge Corner Lot with Fenced Backyard
- No HOA 
- Full Unfinished Basement - Ready for Your Vision
- Ranch-Style Home with Great Bones
- RV Gate and RV Parking Potential
- Wood-Burning Fireplace in Unfinished Basement.


This charming ranch home boasts a nice floorplan with amazing bones, awaiting your personal touch to transform it into your dream home. With a newer stainless steel fridge, a gas stove, and a full tub upstairs, it offers the essentials for comfortable living.

The spacious corner lot provides ample space for outdoor activities and has the potential for an RV gate. Enjoy the natural sledding hill, open space, and gorgeous mountain views nearby, along with easy access to three main parks and a ballfield within walking distance.

Location Highlights:
35 Minutes to Denver Airport
- 25 Minutes to Downtown Denver Sport Arenas
- 5 Minutes to Two Main Hospitals
- 20 Minutes to Downtown Boulder
- 1 Hour and 30 Minutes to Breckenridge

Don't miss the opportunity to make this quaint Broomfield ranch home your own.

Schedule Your Viewing Today!

Act quickly to secure this fantastic property before it's gone. Your charming ranch home in the desirable Broomfield neighborhood awaits! 

* Seller is related to Listing agent
* TLC and new carpet are needed.
